kingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1407022394/image_1407022394.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1407022394/image_1407022394.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1407022394/image_1407022394.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1407022394/image_1407022394.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kevin Dietsch</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Affirm (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AFRM\" title=\"Affirm Holdings, Inc.\">AFRM</a></span>) has been a huge winner as of late. This is in large part due to the company\u2019s strong fundamental performance as management has shown stellar execution amidst challenging macro conditions. I suspect that the stock has</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1407022394/image_1407022394.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742878-affirm-re-evaluating-stock-amidst-top-execution-overheated-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 15:24:36"}, {"id": "4742876", "title": "Silvercorp: Recent Sell-Off Puts The Stock Back Into Buy Territory", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/485703216/image_485703216.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gold &amp; Silver Coins with Silver Bars on map\" data-id=\"485703216\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/485703216/image_485703216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.c