885", "title": "Wall Street Week Ahead", "description": "<div class=\"wsb_wrapper\"> <div class=\"wsb_main\"><span><p class=\"wsb_pb\"><strong>Listen on the go! A daily podcast of Wall Street Breakfast will be available by 8:00 a.m. on <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/wall-street-breakfast?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=toptext&amp;utm_campaign=wsbpodpromo\">Seeking Alpha</a>, <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/wall-street-breakfast/id1358381502\" rel=\"nofollow\">iTunes</a>, <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/05uLjJxkVgQsRk8LWLCLpx\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spotify</a>.</strong></p></span></div> <figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img alt=\"\" data-id=\"2171438579\" data-type=\"getty-image\" height=\"864px\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" width=\"1536px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Sila Damrongsaringkan/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></picture></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div>\n<div class=\"wsb_section\"><div class=\"wsb_mb\"> <p class=\"wsb_pb\"> </p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\">The Fed pendulum swings back to the inflation part of the mandate this week. The November consumer price index hits on Wednesday, just a week before the FOMC's final 2024 meeting.<br><br>Economists expect that headline and core CPI, which excludes food and energy, rose 0.3% last month. In addition, the headline producer price index, which is due Thursday, rose 0.3%, with the core PPI up 0.2%.<br><br>Last week's November payrolls was a Goldilocks number for those hoping for a December rate cut: solid, but not enough to derail the Fed's easing path. The odds of a quarter-point cut rose to 86%.<br><br>Among the big names reporting earnings this week are Oracle (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORCL\" title=\"Oracle Corporation\">ORCL</a>), Adobe (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADBE\" title=\"Adobe Inc.\">ADBE</a>), Broadcom (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO\" title=\"Broadcom Inc.\">AVGO</a>), Costco Wholesale (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COST\" title=\"Costco Wholesale Corporation\">COST</a>), Toll Brothers (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TOL\" title=\"Toll Brothers, Inc.\">TOL</a>) and Ciena (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CIEN\" title=\"Ciena Corporation\">CIEN</a>).<br><br>The Goldman Sachs U.S. Financial Services Conference starts Tuesday and the Barclays 22nd Annual Global Technology Conference begins Wednesday.</p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Earnings spotlight:</strong> Monday, December 9 - Oracle (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORCL\" title=\"Oracle Corporation\">ORCL</a>), Toll Brothers (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TOL\" title=\"Toll Brothers, Inc.\">TOL</a>), and Casey\u2019s General Stores (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CASY\" title=\"Casey's General Stores, Inc.\">CASY</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.<br><br><strong>Earnings spotlight:</strong> Tuesday, December 10 - AutoZone (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AZO\" title=\"AutoZone, Inc.\">AZO</a>), Ferguson Enterprises (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FERG\" title=\"Ferguson Enterprises Inc.\">FERG</a>), GameStop (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GME\" title=\"GameStop Corp.\">GME</a>), Ollie\u2019s Bargain Outlet Holdings (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OLLI\" title=\"Ollie's Bargain Outlet Holdings, Inc.\">OLLI</a>), and Academy Sports and Outdoors (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASO\" title=\"Academy Sports and Outdoors, Inc.\">ASO</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.<br><br><strong>Earnings spotlight: </strong>Wednesday, December 11 - Adobe (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADBE\" title=\"Adobe Inc.\">ADBE</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.<br><br><strong>Earnings spotlight:</strong> Thursday, December 12 - Broadcom (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO\" title=\"Broadcom Inc.\">AVGO</a>), Costco Wholesale (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COST\" title=\"Costco Wholesale Corporation\">COST</a>), and Ciena (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CIEN\" title=\"Ciena Corporation\">CIEN</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"wsb_section\"><div class=\"wsb_mb\"> <p class=\"wsb_bold\">In Case You Missed It ...</p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div>\n<p class=\"wsp-pb\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4362670-markets-stocks-why-you-should-be-checking-reddit-again-ahead-of-trading-meme\">Why you should be checking Reddit again ahead of trading</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4371397-wells-fargos-core-list-googl-dis-hd-wmt-and-more\">Wells Fargo\u2019s \u2018Core\u2019 List</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4359652-15-high-flyer-stocks-that-have-soared-over-100-in-2024-that-still-offer-potential-growth\">15 high flyers that still look cheap</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4367388-11-compounder-opportunities-according-to-goldman-amd-bdx-infa\">11 Compounder opportunities according to Goldman</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4359851-top-quant-rated-cyclical-stocks-as-group-is-expected-to-outperform-in-2025\">Top quant-rated cyclical stocks, as group is expected to outperform in 2025</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4360726-the-top-20-technology-stocks-ranked-by-quant\">Top 20 Technology stocks ranked by Quant</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4365097-what-seeking-alpha-analysts-are-saying-as-bitcoin-trades-above-100000\">What Seeking Alpha analysts are saying as Bitcoin trades above $100K</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4354286-marjorie-taylor-greene-discloses-buys-of-amd-alphabet-microsoft-others\">Marjorie Taylor Greene discloses buys of AMD, Alphabet, Microsoft, others</a></p> </div></div> <div class=\"wsb_pt\"> </div> </div>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742885-wall-street-week-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 15:04:07"}, {"id": "474287